author: odeakin
msg: A few more changes to x-net implementation:
- Modify client auth methods to pass options through to SSL_CTX_set_verify().
- Add initialisation of SSLSessionImpl in terms of SSL_SESSIONs.
- Make sure handshake completion listeners are called once handshaking is successfully completed.
